ou do not feel comfortable with your english grammar and spelling have others preferably native english speakers read over your cover letter any misspellings on a cover letter may cause your application to be immediately discarded personalize your cover letter research the organizations sufficiently so that you can mention your specific interest in the organization in the cover letter learn more about cover letters back to top workshop handouts up interviewing tips groups career development center printer friendly version calendar copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
